WEBVTT

00:02:01.161 --> 00:02:04.680
The factory was so old,
the owners thought it was worthless.

00:02:06.209 --> 00:02:09.271
I thought they left a zero off,

00:02:09.295 --> 00:02:11.229
I couldn't believe the price.

00:02:13.569 --> 00:02:15.442
As I entered in,

00:02:16.331 --> 00:02:20.101
I stopped noticing things.

00:02:20.125 --> 00:02:22.258
All I could see were the people.

00:02:23.897 --> 00:02:25.571
There were 55 of them.

00:02:26.976 --> 00:02:28.126
Just quiet.

00:02:28.738 --> 00:02:32.659
Their only job was
to break the plant apart